---
// SecretsTools.astro — Secrets management tool comparison
---
<div class="stl-wrap">
  <h3 class="stl-title">Tools — Pick Your Vault</h3>
  <div class="stl-grid">
    <details class="stl-card stl-c--purple"><summary class="stl-h"><span class="stl-nm">HashiCorp Vault</span><span class="stl-tag">Self-hosted / HCP</span></summary><div class="stl-body"><p class="stl-p">The gold standard. Dynamic secrets, automatic rotation, lease-based access. Handles every secret type (DB creds, PKI certs, cloud IAM, SSH keys). Complex but comprehensive.</p><div class="stl-pro"><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Dynamic secrets</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Auto-rotation</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--con">Operational complexity</span></div></div></details>
    <details class="stl-card stl-c--amber"><summary class="stl-h"><span class="stl-nm">AWS Secrets Manager</span><span class="stl-tag">Managed</span></summary><div class="stl-body"><p class="stl-p">Tight AWS integration. Automatic rotation for RDS/Redshift. IAM-based access control. Simple but locked to AWS ecosystem.</p><div class="stl-pro"><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Zero ops</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">RDS auto-rotate</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--con">AWS only</span></div></div></details>
    <details class="stl-card stl-c--cyan"><summary class="stl-h"><span class="stl-nm">Doppler</span><span class="stl-tag">SaaS</span></summary><div class="stl-body"><p class="stl-p">Developer-friendly secret syncing. Manages .env replacements across environments. Good DX, weak on dynamic secrets.</p><div class="stl-pro"><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Great DX</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Multi-cloud</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--con">No dynamic secrets</span></div></div></details>
    <details class="stl-card stl-c--green"><summary class="stl-h"><span class="stl-nm">SOPS + Age/KMS</span><span class="stl-tag">GitOps-native</span></summary><div class="stl-body"><p class="stl-p">Encrypt secrets in Git. Decrypt at deploy time. Works with FluxCD/ArgoCD. Secrets live with code (encrypted). Simple, GitOps-friendly.</p><div class="stl-pro"><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">Git-native</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--pro">No extra service</span><span class="stl-t stl-t--con">No rotation</span></div></div></details>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .stl-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .stl-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .stl-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:10px}
  .stl-card{border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #334155;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .3s}
  .stl-c--purple[open]{border-color:#818cf830}.stl-c--amber[open]{border-color:#f59e0b30}.stl-c--cyan[open]{border-color:#06b6d430}.stl-c--green[open]{border-color:#4ade8030}
  .stl-h{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:12px 14px;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15)}.stl-h::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}.stl-h::marker{content:''}
  .stl-nm{color:#e2e8f0;font-weight:700;font-size:.78rem}
  .stl-tag{font-size:.55rem;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:12px;color:#64748b;background:rgba(100,116,139,.1)}
  .stl-body{padding:12px 14px}.stl-p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 8px}
  .stl-pro{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px}
  .stl-t{font-size:.55rem;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:10px;font-family:monospace}.stl-t--pro{color:#4ade80;background:rgba(74,222,128,.08)}.stl-t--con{color:#f87171;background:rgba(248,113,113,.08)}
</style>
